==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superabound
<hw>Su`per*a*bound"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>superabundare</ets>: cf. OF. <ets>superabonder</ets>. See
<er>Super-</er>, and <er>Abound</er>.]</ety> <def>To be very abundant or
exuberant; to be more than sufficient; <as>as, the country
<ex>superabounds</ex> with corn</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superabundance</ent>⟦br⟧
